These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Pet   | snake | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Birthday   | january | february |

 #################################

 
